  "text": "This study contributes to the literature through its dynamic analysis of engaging in marketing activities and its influence on business performance in subsequent years, thus helping to compensate for so few existing longitudinal studies [CITATION_1] ). The analysis model could serve as an example for other longitudinal studies related to other marketing activities or even other general enterprise activities. The results could serve as a starting point for studies analyzing the quality of dialogue with customers in the first year or the quality of engagement in promotional efforts.",
